Enums/UserType.html#/s:5TDLib8UserTypeO7.abstract: A deleted user or deleted bot. No information on the user besides the user_id is available. It is not possible to perform any active actions on this type of user

Enums/UserType.html#/s:5TDLib8UserTypeO7.name: unknown
Enums/UserType.html#/s:5TDLib8UserTypeO7.abstract: No information on the user besides the user_id is available, yet this user has not been deleted. This object is extremely rare and must be handled like a deleted user. It is not possible to perform any actions on users of this type

Enums/UserStatus.html#/s:5TDLib10UserSta.name: lastWeek
Enums/UserStatus.html#/s:5TDLib10UserSta.abstract: The user is offline, but was online last week

Enums/UserStatus.html#/s:5TDLib10UserSta.name: lastMonth
Enums/UserStatus.html#/s:5TDLib10UserSta.abstract: The user is offline, but was online last month

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: allowAll
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to allow all users to do something

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: allowContacts
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to allow all of a user’s contacts to do something

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: allowUsers
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to allow certain specified users to do something

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: restrictAll
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to restrict all users from doing something

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: restrictContacts
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to restrict all contacts of a user from doing something

Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.name: restrictUsers
Enums/UserPrivacySettingRule.html#/s:5TD.abstract: A rule to restrict all specified users from doing something

Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.name: showStatus
Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.abstract: A privacy setting for managing whether the user’s online status is visible

Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.name: allowChatInvites
Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.abstract: A privacy setting for managing whether the user can be invited to chats

Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.name: allowCalls
Enums/UserPrivacySetting.html#/s:5TDLib1.abstract: A privacy setting for managing whether the user can be called

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10new.name: newMessage
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10new.abstract: A new message was received; can also be an outgoing message

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO23mes.name: messageSendAcknowledged
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO23mes.abstract: A request to send a message has reached the Telegram server. This doesn’t mean that the message will be sent successfully or even that the send message request will be processed. This update will be sent only if the option use_quick_ack is set to true. This update may be sent multiple times for the same message

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO17mes.name: messageSendFailed
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO17mes.abstract: A message failed to send. Be aware that some messages being sent can be irrecoverably deleted, in which case updateDeleteMessages will be received instead of this update

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO13mes.name: messageEdited
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO13mes.abstract: A message was edited. Changes in the message content will come in a separate updateMessageContent

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO12mes.name: messageViews
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO12mes.abstract: The view count of the message has changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20mes.name: messageContentOpened
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20mes.abstract: The message content was opened. Updates voice note messages to listened, video note messages to viewed and starts the TTL timer for self-destructing messages

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18mes.name: messageMentionRead
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18mes.abstract: A message with an unread mention was read

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO7newC.name: newChat
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO7newC.abstract: A new chat has been loaded/created. This update is guaranteed to come before the chat identifier is returned to the client. The chat field changes will be reported through separate updates

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO9chat.name: chatTitle
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO9chat.abstract: The title of a chat was changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15cha.name: chatLastMessage
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15cha.abstract: The last message of a chat was changed. If last_message is null then the last message in the chat became unknown. Some new unknown messages might be added to the chat in this case

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO9chat.name: chatOrder
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO9chat.abstract: The order of the chat in the chats list has changed. Instead of this update updateChatLastMessage, updateChatIsPinned or updateChatDraftMessage might be sent

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO13cha.name: chatReadInbox
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO13cha.abstract: Incoming messages were read or number of unread messages has been changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20not.name: notificationSettings
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20not.abstract: Notification settings for some chats were updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15cha.name: chatReplyMarkup
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15cha.abstract: The default chat reply markup was changed. Can occur because new messages with reply markup were received or because an old reply markup was hidden by the user

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16cha.name: chatDraftMessage
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16cha.abstract: A draft has changed. Be aware that the update may come in the currently opened chat but with old content of the draft. If the user has changed the content of the draft, this update shouldn’t be applied

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14use.name: userChatAction
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14use.abstract: User activity in the chat has changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO4user.name: user
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO4user.abstract: Some data of a user has changed. This update is guaranteed to come before the user identifier is returned to the client

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10bas.name: basicGroup
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10bas.abstract: Some data of a basic group has changed. This update is guaranteed to come before the basic group identifier is returned to the client

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10sup.name: supergroup
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10sup.abstract: Some data of a supergroup or a channel has changed. This update is guaranteed to come before the supergroup identifier is returned to the client

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10sec.name: secretChat
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO10sec.abstract: Some data of a secret chat has changed. This update is guaranteed to come before the secret chat identifier is returned to the client

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO12use.name: userFullInfo
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO12use.abstract: Some data from userFullInfo has been changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18bas.name: basicGroupFullInfo
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18bas.abstract: Some data from basicGroupFullInfo has been changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18sup.name: supergroupFullInfo
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18sup.abstract: Some data from supergroupFullInfo has been changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19ser.name: serviceNotification
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19ser.abstract: Service notification from the server. Upon receiving this the client must show a popup with the content of the notification

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19fil.name: fileGenerationStart
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19fil.abstract: The file generation process needs to be started by the client

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO4call.name: call
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO4call.abstract: New call was created or information about a call was updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO23use.name: userPrivacySettingRules
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO23use.abstract: Some privacy setting rules have been changed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18unr.name: unreadMessageCount
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO18unr.abstract: Number of unread messages has changed. This update is sent only if a message database is used

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20ins.name: installedStickerSets
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO20ins.abstract: The list of installed sticker sets was updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19tre.name: trendingStickerSets
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19tre.abstract: The list of trending sticker sets was updated or some of them were viewed

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14rec.name: recentStickers
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14rec.abstract: The list of recently used stickers was updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16fav.name: favoriteStickers
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16fav.abstract: The list of favorite stickers was updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15sav.name: savedAnimations
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO15sav.abstract: The list of saved animations was updated

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.name: newInlineQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.abstract: A new incoming inline query; for bots only

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO21new.name: newChosenInlineResult
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO21new.abstract: The user has chosen a result of an inline query; for bots only

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16new.name: newCallbackQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16new.abstract: A new incoming callback query; for bots only

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO22new.name: newInlineCallbackQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO22new.abstract: A new incoming callback query from a message sent via a bot; for bots only

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16new.name: newShippingQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO16new.abstract: A new incoming shipping query; for bots only. Only for invoices with flexible price

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19new.name: newPreCheckoutQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO19new.abstract: A new incoming pre-checkout query; for bots only. Contains full information about a checkout

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.name: newCustomEvent
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.abstract: A new incoming event; for bots only

Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.name: newCustomQuery
Enums/Update.html#/s:5TDLib6UpdateO14new.abstract: A new incoming query; for bots only

Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.name: users
Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.abstract: A category containing frequently used private chats with non-bot users

Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.name: bots
Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.abstract: A category containing frequently used private chats with bot users

Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.name: groups

Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.name: inlineBots
Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.abstract: A category containing frequently used chats with inline bots sorted by their usage in inline mode

Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.name: calls
Enums/TopChatCategory.html#/s:5TDLib15To.abstract: A category containing frequently used chats used for calls

Enums/TextParseMode.html#/s:5TDLib13Text.name: markdown
Enums/TextParseMode.html#/s:5TDLib13Text.abstract: The text should be parsed in markdown-style

Enums/TextParseMode.html#/s:5TDLib13Text.name: hTML
Enums/TextParseMode.html#/s:5TDLib13Text.abstract: The text should be parsed in HTML-style

Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.name: mention
Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.abstract: A mention of a user by their username

Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.name: cashtag
Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.abstract: A cashtag text, beginning with $ and consisting of capital english letters (i.e. $USD)

Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.name: botCommand
Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.abstract: A bot command, beginning with /. This shouldn’t be highlighted if there are no bots in the chat

Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.name: code
Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.abstract: Text that must be formatted as if inside a code HTML tag

Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.name: pre
Enums/TextEntityType.html#/s:5TDLib14Tex.abstract: Text that must be formatted as if inside a pre HTML tag
